responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "1ADDFEDE4F1B4D17D9377FB68B333877", "Elder meet, we discuss Zinjala's action. After, they return to High Chieftain, as council, help decide punishment. I ask you, Godling, attend moot, not warrior, but symbol. Your presence show not all who come from portal seek harm. Peace still possible, must prove it to my people. Let them see, cooperation with Godling lead future of harmony, no fear.")
